{"tid":1323682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方稱基於公共安全考慮，建議將集會改期至8月","createTime":"2019-07-16T10:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:16:21.000Z","uid":38737,"like":76,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c5e74738398bb0009ae6fa231efe530d927f68","tid":1323682,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"民間人權陣線公告：<br />\n<br />\n民陣原定於7月21日的集會，警方稱基於公共安全考慮，建議將集會改期至8月。民陣表明拒絕，提出反建議在20或21日改為由銅鑼灣遊行到金鐘或中環。召集人岑子杰見記者強調，將集會改為遊行，已是提供彈性予警方考慮。民陣在會上表明將就遊行人士安全作出額外保障，以確保參與人士人身安全，惟詳情有待警方商討落實。<br />\n<br />\n就今個20或21日的行動詳情，民陣已促警方明天必須盡早進行會議，而我們將盡快向大家公佈。"},{"pid":"4068f24e040df2533311f7725378ba2184767d39","tid":1323682,"uid":7954,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5431fdfed80f012f27507f290cbecce1dc957d27","tid":1323682,"uid":276514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑左出黎<br />\n<br />\n冷靜入來睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a0f7c39d5e1ac8509e7094c060d76ade7093a12","tid":1323682,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4068f24e040df2533311f7725378ba2184767d39","tid":1323682,"uid":7954,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},